PROGRAM GeneralizedHandshake
    ARENA my_arena 4096
    WAVELET W1 IN my_arena
    WAVELET W2 IN my_arena
    CONNECT W1 W2

    ! Generalized Trilateral Procedure
    ! GENERATE Rod Cone Domain Link Cost Prime
    GENERATE W1 W2 4919 43690 48059

    IONIZE W1 W2
    MAGNETIZE W1 W2
    
    SEAL_HEADER W1
    SEAL_HEADER W2
    ACTIVATE_YANG W1 12345
    ACTIVATE_YANG W2 12345

    LOG_TELEMETRY "Generalized Handshake Complete"
    PRINT_WAVELET W1
    PRINT_WAVELET W2
END PROGRAM
